                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$\\mathcal{E} = \\frac{I}{L}\\frac{dL}{dt}$!$",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": false
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "27576fb4ffb84940bc462",
                    "stepText": "Great! Now, let's compute the change in inductance using the values given. Recall that $!$\\Delta L = L_{final} - L_{initial}$!$. With $!$L_{initial} = 5\\;\\text{mH}$!$ and $!$L_{final} = 5.01\\;\\text{mH}$!$, calculate $!$\\Delta L$!$ in Henries.",
